            <title>[HBASE-11121] Guidelines on when / how often to do major compaction, as well as default settings and how to change</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11121</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:53:10&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 I&apos;d say 80% of the time you should just let it happen naturally&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:53:26&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 the main thing is deciding how often you want to major compact&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:53:38&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 some people disable it completely because they don&apos;t update/delete&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:53:58&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 others may decide to do it weekly because they don&apos;t update/delete that often&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:54:18&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 and then there&apos;s the aggressive default of doing it every 24h&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:55:39&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 and it looks like the default is now 1 week un trunk&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;14:58:35&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;jdcryans&amp;gt;	 automatic major* compactions&lt;/p&gt;</description>
